title: HELP FIND CULPRIT WHO POURED ACID ON PARKED CAR ON EVE OF CNY
text:
HELP FIND CULPRIT WHO POURED ACID ON PARKED CAR ON EVE OF CNY   Wed, 01/02/2017 - 10:58am 
A lady was shocked to find her car damaged by what appears to be a deliberate act of splashing acid. Advertisement 
She had parked her car at the car park of her estate at 546 Jurong West Street 42. 
She returned to her car to find that the roof of her car was damaged and there was still remnants of the acid on her car window. 
According to her dash-cam, it was visible that someone had poured acid on her car. However, the camera did not capture the person's face. 
The lady has since made a police report. She is appealing for eye-witness to the incident that took place on 28 Jan, Saturday at around 1 am. Editor's Note:
